CREATE TABLE OMDB (
  NAME VARCHAR(50), 
  TYPE VARCHAR(15), 
  CLASS VARCHAR(4), 
  MAX_AIRCRAFT_SIZE VARCHAR(50)
);

  NAME VARCHAR(50),

  NAME VARCHAR(50), 
  TYPE VARCHAR(15), 
  CLASS VARCHAR(4), 
  MAX_AIRCRAFT_SIZE VARCHAR(50)

  NAME VARCHAR(50), 
  TYPE VARCHAR(15), 
  CLASS VARCHAR(4), 
  MAX_AIRCRAFT_SIZE VARCHAR(50)

  NAME VARCHAR(50), 
  TYPE VARCHAR(15), 
  CLASS VARCHAR(4), 
  MAX_AIRCRAFT_SIZE VARCHAR(50)
);

CREATE TABLE WSSS (
  NAME VARCHAR(50), 
  TYPE VARCHAR(15), 
  CLASS VARCHAR(4), 
  MAX_AIRCRAFT_SIZE VARCHAR(50)
);

CREATE TABLE RKSI (
  NAME VARCHAR(50), 
  TYPE VARCHAR(15), 
  CLASS VARCHAR(4), 
  MAX_AIRCRAFT_SIZE VARCHAR(50)
);

CREATE TABLE YSSY (
  NAME VARCHAR(50), 
  TYPE VARCHAR(15), 
  CLASS VARCHAR(4), 
  MAX_AIRCRAFT_SIZE VARCHAR(50)
);

  NAME VARCHAR(50),

  NAME VARCHAR(50), 
  TYPE VARCHAR(15), 
  CLASS VARCHAR(4), 
  MAX_AIRCRAFT_SIZE VARCHAR(50)
);

  NAME VARCHAR(50), 
  TYPE VARCHAR(15), 
  CLASS VARCHAR(4), 
  MAX_AIRCRAFT_SIZE VARCHAR(50)
);

CREATE TABLE VTBS (
  NAME VARCHAR(50), 
  TYPE VARCHAR(15), 
  CLASS VARCHAR(4), 
  MAX_AIRCRAFT_SIZE VARCHAR(50)
);

CREATE TABLE LEBL (
  NAME VARCHAR(50), 
  TYPE VARCHAR(15), 
  CLASS VARCHAR(4), 
  MAX_AIRCRAFT_SIZE VARCHAR(50)
);

  NAME VARCHAR(50), 
  TYPE VARCHAR(15), 
  CLASS VARCHAR(4), 
  MAX_AIRCRAFT_SIZE VARCHAR(50)
);

  NAME VARCHAR(50), 
  TYPE VARCHAR(15), 
  CLASS VARCHAR(4), 
  MAX_AIRCRAFT_SIZE VARCHAR(50)
);

  NAME VARCHAR(50), 
  TYPE VARCHAR(15), 
  CLASS VARCHAR(4), 
  MAX_AIRCRAFT_SIZE VARCHAR(50)
);

  NAME VARCHAR(50),

  NAME VARCHAR(50),

  NAME VARCHAR(50), 
  TYPE VARCHAR(15), 
  CLASS VARCHAR(4), 
  MAX_AIRCRAFT_SIZE VARCHAR(50)
);

CREATE TABLE OTHH (
  NAME VARCHAR(50),

CREATE TABLE LIRF (
  NAME VARCHAR(50), 
  TYPE VARCHAR(15), 
  CLASS VARCHAR(4), 
  MAX_AIRCRAFT_SIZE VARCHAR(50)
);

  NAME VARCHAR(50), 
  TYPE VARCHAR(15), 
  CLASS VARCHAR(4), 
  MAX_AIRCRAFT_SIZE VARCHAR(50)
);

  NAME VARCHAR(50), 
  TYPE VARCHAR(15), 
  CLASS VARCHAR(4), 
  MAX_AIRCRAFT_SIZE VARCHAR(50)
);

CREATE TABLE LKPR (
  NAME VARCHAR(50), 
  TYPE VARCHAR(15), 
  CLASS VARCHAR(4), 
  MAX_AIRCRAFT_SIZE VARCHAR(50)
);

CREATE TABLE LLBG (
  NAME VARCHAR(50), 
  TYPE VARCHAR(15), 
  CLASS VARCHAR(4), 
  MAX_AIRCRAFT_SIZE VARCHAR(50)
);

  NAME VARCHAR(50), 
  TYPE VARCHAR(15), 
  CLASS VARCHAR(4), 
  MAX_AIRCRAFT_SIZE VARCHAR(50)
);

  NAME VARCHAR(50), 
  TYPE VARCHAR(15),

  MAX_AIRCRAFT_SIZE VARCHAR(50)

  NAME VARCHAR(50), 
  TYPE VARCHAR(15), 
  CLASS VARCHAR(4), 
  MAX_AIRCRAFT_SIZE VARCHAR(50)
);
